                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d370">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">033.60C11/61c: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé Near the Polish Government in Exile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schoenfeld</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">at London</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-28T21:00:00-04:00"
                            >December 28, 1943—9 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>[Polish Series No.] 40. Please deliver the following message from the President
                    to Prime Minister Mikolajczyk: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“In view of recent developments Prime Minister Churchill has suggested
                            that he believes it might be advisable for you to postpone your trip to
                            Washington until you have had an opportunity to talk with him.</p>
                        <p>As I feel that you too will wish to have such an opportunity for a
                            personal discussion with Mr. Churchill I have informed him that I too
                            think it best to have a postponement. I am sure that you will concur in
                            this decision, and I am looking forward to the pleasure of seeing you as
                            soon as your talks with him are finished.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
